1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,320
I remember, and then she heard it, a voice, cold and cruel echoing in the room.

2
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:09,080
You will be punished, and you will join the jewellery in the box.

3
00:00:09,080 --> 00:00:14,680
I remember you are a despicable human who deserves to be punished, cat screamed.

4
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:19,440
I remember the creature released Sharon disappearing before their mother ran in and turned

5
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:20,640
on the lights.

6
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:23,400
I remember, but the fear lingered.

7
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:26,360
I remember every shadow in the room felt alive.

8
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:28,960
I remember every corner seemed to watch.

9
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:33,920
I remember their mother led them outside to the car, but none of them slept that night.

10
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:38,240
I remember somewhere just outside the window the figure watched.

11
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:42,840
I remember the next morning as the beds were being taken down, their mother found something

12
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:46,280
under cat and Sharon's bed, a jewellery box.

13
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:48,000
I remember it hadn't been there before.
